<L>__{interior locker room wash a rama day}
<A>__{tight, shabby facilities. dan opens the combination padlock to his locker and deposits the crumpled photo inside. as the hands remove the rubber gloves, the inside of the locker is revealed. pasted over every inch of the locker are pictures of rachel marron. one tabloid shot of her dancing with the word "whore" scrawled across it. taped to a single sheet of white paper in the center, like a holy relic, is the torn scrap of rachel's dress from the mayan. the hands pin up the newly acquired photo next to it.}
